1303   // (X == C) && (Y Pred1 X) --> (X == C) && (Y Pred1 C)
1304   // (X != C) || (Y Pred1 X) --> (X != C) || (Y Pred1 C)
1305   // Can think of the 'or' substitution with the 'and' bool equivalent:
1306   // A || B --> A || (!A && B)
